(12013092,8,'{\"text\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"<p>The KC-390 platform provides unmatched versatility to configure the aircraft to accomplish a broader range of missions. </p>\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>One aircraft, many capabilities.</p>\"}}}',NULL,0,'2018-05-10 15:31:08',NULL),
(12013093,8,'{\"text\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"<h3 class=\\\"-heading -tp1\\\">Truly multi-mission aircraft</h3>\"}}}',NULL,0,'2018-05-10 15:31:08',NULL),
(12013094,11,'{\"slides\": [{\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/43d6e23d62ea8a5e/original/KC-390.jpg\", \"name\": \"KC-390\", \"tags\": [\"KC-390\", \"Embraer Defense & Security\"], \"bynderId\": \"4B187749-D50C-444F-94D017981DB700E3\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Quick configuration\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Reducing time on the ground and in the air will deliver mission success and help save lives. The KC-390 can be reconfigured for all missions in 3 hours or less.    \"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/3c3ed0e3490f36cb/original/cargo_handling.jpg\", \"name\": \"cargo_handling\", \"tags\": [\"KC-390\", \"Embraer Defense & Security\"], \"bynderId\": \"4C2E706F-2F85-4DFD-879C79A61DEA9017\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Advanced cargo handling system\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"The advanced Cargo Handling System (CHS) provides high flexibility and productivity levels, merging a modern solution for software controlled cargo locking and proven cargo handling mechanical solutions. The CHS is designed to be easily and quickly reconfigured for different missions without the need of special tools. The cargo floor can be changed from flat to a roller configuration with the flip-over capability.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/504ff8e45d79b18d/original/flexibility.jpg\", \"name\": \"flexibility\", \"tags\": [\"KC-390\", \"Embraer Defense & Security\"], \"bynderId\": \"F462F66B-A5E1-4A1C-821A8A0B70979894\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Robustness & flexibility\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"The cargo floor, an integral part of the KC-390 main structure, is designed with the strength to transport heavy-tracked and wheeled vehicles of up to 26,000 kg (57,320 lb). An optimized tie-down grid of rings with 10,000 lb and 25,000 lb of restraint in any direction ensures quick configurations changes and great cargo load flexibility. The CHS features all the necessary accessories to facilitate cargo loading, restraining and offloading, such as tie-down rings, roller trays, cargo guidance and restraint systems. It is fully compatible with the existing military airlift equipment, such as type V platforms, 463L pallets, A-22 CDS bundles and ground support loaders. \"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/69ca3c597bbe7597/original/KC-390-Back-View.jpg\", \"name\": \"KC-390-Back-View\", \"tags\": [\"flight\"], \"bynderId\": \"7D617549-EAD5-424A-94FBEFA8A5033A01\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"From fast jets to helicopters \"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Advanced design\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Day and night aerial refueling capability with observer windows and night vision cameras. e KC-390 has advanced refueling pods (912E) that meet the high performance criteria of the aircraft providing a lightweight and efficient solution. Each pod provides fuel transfer up to 400 USgpm. Removable auxiliary fuel tanks can be installed in the fuselage to expand the aircraft fuel offload capacity or range performance. \"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/2fec5d02338bb494/original/KC-390-AAR-REVO_001-FOTO-REAL-.jpg\", \"name\": \"KC-390 AAR REVO_001 (FOTO REAL)\", \"tags\": [\"defesa e segurança\", \"flight\", \"Embraer Defense & Security\"], \"bynderId\": \"F10EBE5F-62AA-4245-8AE080845538C804\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Aerial refueling high & low speed\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"The KC-390 is capable of refueling both fixed and rotary wing aircraft, operating at speeds from 120 KCAS to 300 KCAS and at altitudes from 2,000 ft to 32,000 ft. The KC-390 on ground refueling capability also serves Ground forces with vehicles or advance bases refueling. \"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/2322c6180f7673f3/original/KC-390-Campo-Grande-Salto-Rampa-e-Porta-11.jpg\", \"name\": \"KC-390 Campo Grande - Salto Rampa e Porta 11\", \"tags\": [\"Campo Grande\", \"Parashoot\", \"flight\"], \"bynderId\": \"3A33B5A0-25D5-4DE8-99A63DC71C748ED6\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Air drop effectiveness & precision\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"The KC-390 aerial delivery system provides remote and automatic release of cargo in hight at low and high altitudes. The KC-390 is capable of: LVAD* type-V platforms (single and multiple) up to 41,887 lb; Aerial delivery of CDS (Container Delivery System) up to 41,887 lb; Low Altitude Parachute Extraction (LAPES) up to 22,046 lb.  * Low Velocity Aerial Delivery \"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/64466fab565bac64/original/search_rescue_the_first_responder.jpg\", \"name\": \"search_rescue_the_first_responder\", \"bynderId\": \"646A1D40-9275-4A91-8BA723EA09BAEA87\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Search & rescue. The true first responder.\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"During Search & Rescue missions, every minute counts to save lives. The KC-390 turbo fan engines provide unmatched speed compared with other aircraft in the medium lift segment. The KC-390 can be equipped with a complete set of equipment to support Search&Rescue missions: Removable Electro-Optical/Infrared pod (EO/IR); Four spotter positions; Lateral litters and/or crew seats; Removable internal fuel tanks to expand range or time on station.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/0ef151652f5dac68/original/aeromedical_evacuation.jpg\", \"name\": \"aeromedical_evacuation\", \"bynderId\": \"87D20C7A-605B-42FE-86915B1476753716\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Aeromedical evacuation\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \" The KC-390 provides support for ground operations or disaster relief missions transporting wounded survivors or casualties.  e KC-390 can be con gured to carry up to 74 litters (STANAG 2040) and 8 additional members, including medical attendants and necessary life supporting equipment. The KC-390 can be configured to carry up to 74 litters. \"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/5164ab1f4f24b589/original/aerial_firefighting.jpg\", \"name\": \"aerial_firefighting\", \"bynderId\": \"3928227B-56DF-4307-B2E74542E7F9C5C7\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Aerial firefighting\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"When equipped with a roll-on-roll-off firefighting system, the KC-390 is an important aerial resource for firefighters in battling wildfires, dropping water or fire retardants. The KC-390 fly-by-wire provides outstanding maneuverability at low speed and low altitude to fly over wildfire areas, increasing the mission efficiency.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/4124d85049771b53/original/kc_390_combat_ops.jpg\", \"name\": \"kc_390_combat_ops\", \"tags\": [\"KC390\", \"defesa e segurança\", \"Embraer Defense & Security\"], \"bynderId\": \"99D6FFE6-323A-4B96-8C0D5AC022719C0F\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Self protection suite\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"The KC-390 can be equipped with a complete self protection suite (SPS) to increase survivability levels. Detection & Countermeasures with 360° coverage: Radar Warning Receiver (RWR) Laser Warning System (LWS) Missile Approach Warning System (MAWS) Chaff & Flare Directional Infrared Counter Measures (DIRCM). Electro Optics/Infrared Pod; Ballistic Protection (Armor 7.62 mm and 0.50 inch); Enhanced Vision System (EVS); HALO Oxygen Rack. \"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"\", \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Survivability \"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Basic characteristics of KC-390 design also increase the aircraft survivability level.  Key Points:  High Speed similar to a fast jet: Mach 0.8; High Altitude: 36,000 ft; Fuel Tanks Inertization: OBIGGS; Redundancy and segregation for critical systems; Night Vision Compatibility; Tactical Radar.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}]}',NULL,0,'2018-05-10 15:31:08',NULL),
(12013095,11,'{\"slides\": [{\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/263bfd9150c0468f/original/cockpit_kc_390_real.jpg\", \"name\": \"cockpit_kc_390_real\", \"tags\": [\"defesa e segurança\", \"KC 390\", \"Embraer Defense & Security\", \"cockpit\"], \"bynderId\": \"08D3C5D9-1B47-4B90-9640DF4D6FCDB898\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \" \"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"State of the art technology\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Building over decades of development experience, the KC-390 incorporates the most advanced and proven technologies and design concepts. Equipped with state-of-the-art technologies, the KC-390 provides significant reduced crew workload, efficiency and precision for the accomplishment of mission.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/1f557fa838c25109/original/fly_by_wire.jpg\", \"name\": \"fly_by_wire\", \"bynderId\": \"D5B29F92-34E3-4A89-A5E26DB893625DC2\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \" \"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Fly-by-wire\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \" The most capable flight control system in the segment allowing pilots to tailor the system to the mission and safely  y to the limits of the flight envelope with low crew workload.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/4df4f8af0550529a/original/Teste-de-Icone-de-Defesa.jpg\", \"name\": \"Teste de Icone de Defesa\", \"bynderId\": \"3784E7F8-5F8D-4698-A796FA90472CCF04\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \" \"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Avionics\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Fully interactive and CNS/ATM compliant Rockwell Collins Pro Line Fusion Suite delivers intuitive Human Machine Interfaces, enhancing productivity and safety.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/7d8afc9b006989a0/original/oacms.jpg\", \"name\": \"oacms\", \"bynderId\": \"19260A90-CDFB-4DB1-8EB06DBE01135A3F\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \" \"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Optional additional crew member station\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"An optional third crew station in the cockpit, equipped with an integrated display, communication system and mission controls, supports efficient coordination on advanced missions including Search and Rescue and Aerial Refueling.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/1b31eaba0ec447cc/original/evs_svs.jpg\", \"name\": \"evs_svs\", \"bynderId\": \"2967AD8F-CFC8-42F0-8350EBA2E30890F9\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \" \"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"EVS/SVS\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Dual Head-up Displays with Enhanced Vision System have significantly improved situational awareness in critical operational scenarios, such as in low visibility conditions.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/2e28ef034b0af2ec/original/oms.jpg\", \"name\": \"oms\", \"bynderId\": \"3FBEF7A1-548E-4273-AE417D4271017809\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \" \"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"OMS\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"A fully integrated Onboard Maintenance System provides diagnostic information to the maintenance crews, facilitating troubleshooting activities, reducing downtime and cost and achieving airline level availability.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/4fe7a4ff1a9f1d8a/original/advanced_chs.jpg\", \"name\": \"advanced_chs\", \"bynderId\": \"7C5C9214-ECDB-4266-B20180A1C331C9D7\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \" \"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Advanced CHS\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \" The Flexible Cargo Handling System (CHS) supports the handling of a wide range of cargo in different configurations. This supports ease of load and unload of vehicles and pallets. It also supports automatic cargo aerial delivery.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/72ef6fc975be3bbb/original/loadmaster.jpg\", \"name\": \"loadmaster\", \"bynderId\": \"D84D45D2-1B69-44E3-AC4E14E70A20758F\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \" \"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Loadmaster station\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"From a protected station, the Loadmaster can control and operate the Cargo Handling System, enhancing system situational awareness and allowing efficient handing and deployment of cargo.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/5486f79d72cd5921/original/strut.jpg\", \"name\": \"strut\", \"bynderId\": \"F6655A51-C3A9-4ECF-82C0BC6A6268BC6A\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \" \"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Strut stabilizer \"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \" The Hydraulic Strut Stabilizer is an important feature for remote and autonomous operation. Commanded from the Loadmaster Station, it conveniently stabilizes the aircraft reducing time on the ground and minimizing vulnerability in hostile environments.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/7ef7d64165f1bac1/original/wheels.jpg\", \"name\": \"wheels\", \"bynderId\": \"3DA6720A-A9C8-451A-89EE0C3072C5EA8D\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \" \"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Four wheels bogie type main landing gear\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"A Four Wheel Bogie Type Main Landing Gear provides efficient flotation capabilities for operations on soft air fields (CBR-4) as well as shock absorbing capabilities for operations on damaged runways. It supports deployment of the aircraft to unassisted and remote locations.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/419d61cd39984d86/original/comfort.jpg\", \"name\": \"comfort\", \"bynderId\": \"BD5EB5D9-9BA4-4F95-881CEA1980FD844B\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \" \"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Comfort\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \" The KC-390 Air Conditioning and Pressurization System are modern and efficient, with precise temperature and low cabin altitude controls: when with the aircraft’s wider cross section and a heated floor in the cargo compartment, comfort is enhanced during Medevac and Troop Transport Missions.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/2146bac86353dbc3/original/radar.jpg\", \"name\": \"radar\", \"bynderId\": \"C2FEB363-B0A1-4073-99EA7AC12BA4295B\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \" \"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Tactical radar\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"The KC-390 is equipped with advanced Tactical Radar, featuring Spot SAR (Spotlight Synthetic Aperture Radar), weather, air-to-air, navigation, air-to-ground and high resolution modes.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/56bf0f7c4f6964ab/original/protection.jpg\", \"name\": \"protection\", \"bynderId\": \"5E43B9BD-C1FF-4159-B6FEE4A698317C04\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \" \"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Self protection\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \" The KC-390 Self-Protection System combines a broad range of Detection & Declaration devices (Radar Warning, Laser Warning and Missile Approach Warning) to capable Countermeasures (Chaff and Flare and DIRCM); enhancing the aircraft security in hostile scenarios.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/1065da4523c90c55/original/mission_systems.jpg\", \"name\": \"mission_systems\", \"bynderId\": \"7AED8DB2-CC93-499F-9907F51F5A6111F9\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Mission systems\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \" The KC-390 integrates several mission systems to provide truly advanced multi-mission capabilities. Tactical SAR Radar, EO/IR Probe and Mission Computers allow the flexible employment of the aircraft to dfferent scenarios.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/2f84d18658d6b9fd/original/ccdp.jpg\", \"name\": \"ccdp\", \"bynderId\": \"DB9A5199-A675-4BC7-8BA6EC028E2B9A00\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"CCDP\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"For the air delivery mission, the Continuous Computed Drop Point (CCDP) algorithm uses altitude, speed and wind to define the optimum release point to reach the drop zone. This allows for manual or automatic cargo release.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/7b63750a76aaa120/original/nvis.jpg\", \"name\": \"nvis\", \"bynderId\": \"D06CAEB2-3840-435D-A2E44EA99AA4676B\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"NVIS\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \" The KC-390 interior, exterior and cockpit systems are fully Night Vision compatible.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}]}',NULL,0,'2018-05-10 15:31:08',NULL),
