,(12013098,11,'{\"slides\": [{\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"\", \"bynderId\": \"BB19576D-AC5C-429C-A4EAC2A3125AF6CE\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Designed to operate in short, austere and semi-prepared runways.\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Developed according to stringent requirements, the KC-390 is a multi-mission aircraft, with a rugged design that withstands operations from semi-prepared and damaged runways, as well as in harsh environments, varying from the hot and humid Amazon forest down to the freezing cold Antarctic continent, as well as in hot and sandy desert conditions.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"\", \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \" \"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Small, austere and semi-prepared air fields are important operational environments for military airlift aircraft.  The operational capacity of the KC-390 on semi-prepared and unpaved air fields is achieved with a highly capable structure, * Critical Field Length landing gear designed to operate and reduce damage on soft unpaved air fields.  e engines are mounted in a forward elevated position to prevent ingress from debris.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/59625464490266d5/original/KC-390-NZ-pista-gelo_02.jpg\", \"name\": \"KC-390 NZ - pista gelo_02\", \"bynderId\": \"6793F0D3-1117-4098-B5808761736D2560\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"  \"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \" The KC-390 is capable of operating from the maximum (worst) semi-prepared runway de ned by MIL-A-008866B and, for soft field operations, perform 10 passes at a CBR 4 air eld (loose fine sand or soft clay). The KC-390 has excellent ground maneuverability, and can operate on air fields with limited space for parking or maneuvering and no ground facilities.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"\", \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \" \"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \" The KC-390 can normally operate from a 4,000 ft (CFL*) semi-prepared soft airstrip (CBR-6: compacted sand-clay soils) carrying 12 metric ton of cargo to a distance of 500 nm. Damage Tolerant Design: Modern structural design - strong and durable airframe.  IAE V2500 Engine:  Minimum FOD ingestion. Optimum position (high clearance and forward mounted). Wide chord metallic fan blades. Part 33 Certified Engine. Antartic Operation: Operational from an unpaved runway covered with ice and snow on the freezing cold Antarctic continent.  Semi-Prepared Operation: Worst Semi-Prepared Runway from MIL 8866B. Landing Gear:  Low Resistance Airfields (CBR-4) Brake-by-Wire, Wheel-by-Wheel. All Weather: Designed for extreme climates, including hot and sandy desert conditions.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}]}',NULL,0,'2018-05-10 15:31:08',NULL),
(12013099,11,'{\"slides\": [{\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/4f33607025344fec/original/lifeciclecost.jpg\", \"name\": \"lifeciclecost\", \"bynderId\": \"583AFE27-5587-41CF-AF421D9E480A75A5\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Life cycle cost\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Outstanding Cargo Capacity, Speed and Availability result in incomparable productivity, which when associated with autonomous operational capabilities, lead to reduced and affordable Life Cycle Costs.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/58803c8351c1bc26/original/KC-390_marco2018_001.JPG\", \"name\": \"KC-390_marco2018_001\", \"tags\": [\"ground\", \"detail\"], \"bynderId\": \"0B0B0E20-F9B5-425A-90366E872CF3FD89\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Reliability\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"KC-390 incorporates recognized proven technologies to redundant systems architectures, leading to unprecedented reliability levels in the segment.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/3954ff114ecdf858/original/maintability.jpg\", \"name\": \"maintability\", \"bynderId\": \"8D2CB46C-798A-488B-8E610F602081FDEC\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Maintainability \"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \" The KC-390 design has maintainability as a major requirement. Employing the most effcient methods, such as MSG-3, tools and experience, the aircraft’s maintenance is substantially facilitated and optimized to a minimize downtime and cost.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/6f66b11120f74bb0/original/maintenance_plan.jpg\", \"name\": \"maintenance_plan\", \"bynderId\": \"860BFBEB-C9EE-4BC0-A35021D62B1276AC\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Maintenance plan\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Besides reducing downtime, the optimized Maintenance Plan enhances the bene ts of high reliability systems and the airframe; strategically combining the necessary inspections, checks and services in a most productive logic. Interactions with air forces, systems manufacturers and certification authorities in Maintenance Steering Groups leveraged real maintenance experience in the development process.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/7e9f5d5e6dfce2a2/original/aviability.jpg\", \"name\": \"aviability\", \"bynderId\": \"EBBB328E-8AE2-43F0-9D91D55B10D4C5F9\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Availability\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \" The highest levels of reliability, combined with ease of maintenance delivers unparalleled availability in the medium airlift market. The optimized maintenance planning and on condition maintenance reduce substantially aircraft downtime and maintenance costs.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}]}',NULL,0,'2018-05-10 15:31:08',NULL),
(12013100,11,'{\"slides\": [{\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/77d2875d43ffa5ac/original/Foto-do-Moço-no-Hangar.jpg\", \"name\": \"Foto do Moço no Hangar\", \"tags\": [\"Hangar\", \"KC-390\", \"Embraer Defense & Security\"], \"bynderId\": \"C886F9E1-3AFB-4D04-A7AB3DDC5AF73D3D\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Logistic support & training\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Embraer training infrastructure or on site training devices can be used for expedited operational and maintenance crew readiness. Unprecedented reliability levels for the segment, associated with a design optimized to reduce maintenance and combined with comprehensive support and material services support solutions.  This delivers very high fleet availability and low life cycle.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/76cea71f1b0a3483/original/material_services.jpg\", \"name\": \"material_services\", \"bynderId\": \"B680A62D-CE17-4037-8763EEB6CD238EC5\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Material services\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Supply chain solutions, from transactional to outcome based supply packages. Including: parts, component repairs and support equipment. Utilizing our vast Global network providing Repair & Overhaul, Logistics operations, Stock Optimization and Warehouse management.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/6dd5a75109489a81/original/fleet_services.jpg\", \"name\": \"fleet_services\", \"bynderId\": \"E9554A5C-07E4-40BF-913E70631008ADD7\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Fleet services\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Specialized Entry to Service Team assuring mission readiness upon initial operation. World class on-site field service representatives assuring fleet readiness anytime, anywhere. Continued sustaining support with scalable optimized maintenance solutions.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/464c0b4c42ba984d/original/flight_services_training.jpg\", \"name\": \"flight_services_training\", \"bynderId\": \"4C3CFDD4-D55A-4796-A2DFDB5F8E1555D0\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Flight services and training\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Specialized Center providing Flight, Maintenance, and Specialized operator training solutions for initial and continued training needs.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/50f5486d36c375c6/original/field_services.jpg\", \"name\": \"field_services\", \"bynderId\": \"489D3B35-D35A-4ECB-BEE1CD4852D6EA66\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Field services\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Specialized field service technicians teamed with each Customer to maximize aircraft value thought out the entire life cycle. Providing scalable sustainment solutions, from basic to turn-key performance based capabilities and services.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}, {\"type\": \"image\", \"image\": {\"url\": \"https://daflwcl3bnxyt.cloudfront.net/m/0437987d097c55da/original/information_services.jpg\", \"name\": \"information_services\", \"bynderId\": \"83F7FFC7-0CD4-4A3F-9F4E14BB314A1AD1\"}, \"label\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"title\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Information services\"}}, \"btnurl\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"btnlabel\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"\"}}, \"description\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"Complete state-of-the-art information technology capability services to insure current, timely, and accurate information needed to keep the flight, operations, and maintenance crews equipped and informed at all times.\"}}, \"remove_overlay\": 0}]}',NULL,0,'2018-05-10 15:31:08',NULL),
(12013101,8,'{\"text\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"<p>The KC-390 is undergoing a full military certification process built over a dual certification approach from beginning. This hybrid process combines the efforts of both civil and military airworthiness authorities. This approach ensures the aircraft can safely accomplish all its military missions. The KC-390 basic platform is being developed and  certified by the Brazilian civil airworthiness authority in accordance with FAA 14 CFR Part 25 standards. The military certification complements the civil certification with military standards, specifications and criteria in order to cover the military mission accomplishment, military items and systems.<br></p>\"}}}',NULL,0,'2018-05-10 15:31:08',NULL),
