(12013324,8,'{\"text\": {\"_text\": {\"en\": \"<p>The Phenom 300 MEDEVAC is an excellent solution derived from the Phenom 300 aircraft with modifications to make it suitable for medical evacuation services. The LifePortTM PLUS platform installed on this aircraft provides:</p><p>• Ramp load system<br>• Stretcher<br>• Mounts for medical equipment<br>• Electrical inverter (1,000-watt, 115 vac, 60 hz)<br>• Control panel with multiple functions<br>• Oxygen (8,500 liters on total) <br>• Compressed air pump.</p>\"}}}',NULL,0,'2018-05-11 14:44:42',NULL),
